These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, musical, thriller
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, orchid, amaryllis, marigold
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the person who growsorchid is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
5. the person who growsmarigold is between the person who growsorchid and the person who growsamaryllis##2
6. the person watching thriller movies is the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | crime     | musical | disaster |
| Flower     | rose     | amaryllis | marigold  | orchid      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
City: hannover, san-francisco, berlin, paris
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, snowmobile, trike
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person traveling to berlin is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| City   | hannover | san-francisco    | paris     | berlin  |
| Transport     | bus    | snowmobile | helicopter | trike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, whist, billiard, snooker
4 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, rabbit, snake
1. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
2. the person playing whist is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Game   | whist   | billiard   | monopoly  | snooker |
| Pet           | lizard | snake | rabbit | cat  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, collecting, dancing, fishing
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, january, february, august
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's birthday is in february##2
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | collecting | board-games | fishing | dancing  |
| Birthday   | january  | september   | august  | february |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
City: hannover, london, new-york, boston
1. the person traveling to london is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person traveling to boston is the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | 7up    | fanta   | hot-chocolate | soy-milk    |
| City      | london | hannover | new-york       | boston |

