.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, juice, soy-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, librarian, firefighter, photographer
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the firefighter is between the photographer and the person drinking juice##2
3. the security-guard is between the firefighter and the person drinking coffee##2
4. the photographer is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | coffee | juice | soy-milk | fanta |
| Job   | librarian | security-guard  | firefighter    | photographer  |

