3. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
4. the indian is between the french and the thai##2
5. the person traveling to boston is the person traveling to boston##1
6. the person traveling to boston is between the person traveling to hamburg and the thai##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Nationality   | egyptian | thai | indian | french     |
| City     | rome | liverpool  | boston   | hamburg |

