There 4 different types of food: peach, pineapple, onion, garlic
1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person eating peach##1
2. the person eating garlic is on the far right##1
3. the person eating garlic is the owner of the snake##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the fish is between the person eating pineapple and the person eating peach##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet     | chinchilla | fish   | horse      | snake      |
| Food   | pineapple     | onion | peach | garlic |

