.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, electronic, jazz, salsa
4 different games are played: canasta, bridge, go, domino
1. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
2. the fan of jazz is between the person playing domino and the person playing bridge##2
3. the fan of electronic is the person playing bridge##1
4. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
5. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | classical | electronic | jazz      | salsa   |
| Game   | go  | bridge    | canasta | domino |

