2. the tower house is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
3. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
4. the tower house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| House   | ranch-style | tower | art-deco | modern |
| Sport         | parkour  | rugby   | soccer | golf     |

