.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-18::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, september, august, october
4 different pets are kept: cat, dog, guinea-pig, hamster
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is the owner of the hamster##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left or far right##3
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person who's birthday is in october and the owner of the hamster##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |  4  |
| Birthday   | august | september  | january  | october |
| Pet           | cat    | hamster | guinea-pig | dog |

